Variables: student name, baseUrl, confirmation number (appointment id), advisor, location

Confirmation/Reminder:

$firstName,

You have an appointment on $date at $time with $advisor in $location.

Click <a href=”$baseUrl/delete.html?confirmation=$confirmationNumber”>here</a> to cancel your appointment.


Student canceled:

$advisor,

Unfortunately, $studentName is unable to make it to the appointment scheduled on $date at $time.


Advisor canceled:

$firstName,

Unfortunately, $advisor is unable to attend your appointment on $date at $time. Please reschedule at $baseUrl.
